Enum EffectCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EffectCode>
      • constants.EffectCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnumValue, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EffectCode>

    public enum EffectCode
extends java.lang.Enum<EffectCode>
implements EnumValue
    Effect codes used in an Effect entry. They defines the action to execute.
    Author:
    MarcoForlini
